  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support%20me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join%20our%20Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Join our Discord\"></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support%20me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a></p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cw/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/49b1e899a9f41e7eeeb877bc53e8d5838998a95b_0.webp\" alt=\"Patreon\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n# Auto Builder\nautomatically place blocks while walking forward\n\n![1](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/o8SP0vwL/images/7a67065f4fe8e3f3e1256d181a17c81988fa82c2.gif)\n\n**How to use**   \njump and sneak at the same time when you have a placeable block in you hand\n\nPlaceable Blocks >>>\n- Stone, Cobblestone, Netherrack, End Stone\n- All Wood Planks (Oak, Spruce, Birch, Jungle, Acacia, Dark Oak)\n- Dirt, Grass Block\n- Sandstone, Red Sandstone\n- Glass\n- Bricks\n- Quartz Block\n- Terracotta\n- White Concrete, Black Concrete",
